## 13. Tailwind Config Additions

Add these to `tailwind.config.ts` to use tokens as Tailwind classes:

```ts
theme: {
  extend: {
    colors: {
      cream:    "#FAF6EF",
      "cream-deep": "#F0E8DA",
      ink:      "#1C1917",
      "ink-soft":  "#44403C",
      "ink-muted": "#78716C",
      gold:     "#C8952A",
      "gold-light": "#F5DFA0",
      "gold-dark":  "#8B6318",
    },
    fontFamily: {
      display: ["var(--font-display)", "Georgia", "serif"],
      sans:    ["var(--font-sans)", "system-ui", "sans-serif"],
      mono:    ["var(--font-mono)", "monospace"],
    },
    boxShadow: {
      gold: "0 4px 20px rgba(200,149,42,0.25)",
    },
  },
}
```

---

## 14. Page-by-Page Checklist

When updating each of your 10‚Äì15 files, go through this in order:

1. **Replace** all `bg-[#F5E6D3]` / `bg-[#FDB913]` ‚Üí `bg-cream` / `bg-gold`
2. **Replace** all `text-[#1A1A1A]` ‚Üí `text-ink`
3. **Replace** `font-black` on headings ‚Üí `font-display font-bold` or `font-black`
4. **Replace** `Arial Black` / `Impact` inline styles ‚Üí `font-display` class
5. **Replace** emoji placeholders in cards ‚Üí warm gradient divs
6. **Replace** rotated badges ‚Üí clean `font-mono uppercase` spans
7. **Check** all buttons match the component spec above
8. **Check** all inputs have the correct focus ring (`ring-gold`)
9. **Add** `leading-tight` to all display headings
10. **Verify** section alternates between `bg-cream` and `bg-cream-deep` (not random colors)

---

## 15. Anti-Patterns (Never Do)

- ‚ùå `font-family: Impact` or `Arial Black` anywhere
- ‚ùå `transform: rotate(Xdeg)` on text badges
- ‚ùå `bg-[#FDB913]` ‚Äî use `bg-gold` token
- ‚ùå Emoji as UI icons (`üî•`, `üì±`, `‚≠ê`)
- ‚ùå `text-[80px]` hardcoded ‚Äî use `clamp()` or scale tokens
- ‚ùå `transition: all` ‚Äî always specify property
- ‚ùå Multiple accent colors in one section
- ‚ùå `font-bold` on body copy (only `font-medium` or `font-semibold` max)
- ‚ùå Inline `style={{ color: "#1A1A1A" }}` ‚Äî use Tailwind classes from the token map

